==Description== <!--T:3-->

<!--T:4-->
The [[Image:Curves_Line.svg|24px]] [[Curves_Line|Curves Line]] creates a parametric line between two vertices. This tool is part of the [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] called [[Curves_Workbench|Curves]].

